data.description: Welcome to Paradise! You CAN Have It ALL! Spacious Single Family Home in Colony Woods-Boca's Hidden Gem. This quiet 55+ Community, located in the heart of Boca, offers the perfect lifestyle. No worries w/full impact protection, newer A/C, & the perfect floor plan to create your dream home for the next chapter. Entertain family & friends w/your large eat-in kitchen, formal dining room, living room & bonus Florida room. Enjoy your ample primary suite, w/closet space galore & spacious primary bath. The large second bedroom & full size bathroom offer many options. The 3rd bedroom is being used as an office-den, w/plenty of space to sleep guests. Enjoy your private, oversized corner lot, & become the envy of your new neighbors. Imagine the possibilities, & make Colony Woods Your New Home!
